Ikkada: Course name repeated
Instructor repeated

Step 1 - 1NF: Already atomic
Step 2 - 2NF: Primary key = (student_id, course_id)
course_name -> depends only on course_id
Step 3 - 3NF: Instructor depends on course → transitive dependency

Final Solution entante:
Students
